377
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:27,680
From that moment on,

378
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:30,200
a friendship of ten years...

379
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,400
Brother Xiao Han,

380
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:43,640
I'll soon have a computer too.

381
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,720
When you're in high school,

382
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,200
