385
00:22:53,030 --> 00:22:54,000
Chen Mo?

386
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,550
Does Brother Xiao Han know her?

387
00:22:57,550 --> 00:22:58,440
Brother Xiao Han,

388
00:22:58,440 --> 00:22:59,440
