389
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,280
Did you lose it?

390
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:03,350
No wonder you're upset.

391
00:23:03,350 --> 00:23:04,300
Mind your own business.

392
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:28,980
(Shanghai Puyang Central Hospital)

393
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:47,510
A doctor's handwriting

394
00:23:47,510 --> 00:23:49,830
