395
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,000
Han.

396
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,240
Have some food.

397
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:00,160
You skipped dinner.

398
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:02,440
After this bottle, there are two more.

399
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,960
At least two hours to go.

400
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:11,440
Your 16th birthday
is coming up next month.

401
00:24:12,350 --> 00:24:15,590
You're not a kid anymore.

402
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:19,200
There's something
I've wanted to tell you,

403
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,680
but your mom wouldn't let me.

404
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,550
She's afraid you'll get upset.

405
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,750
Let's put aside your reaction.

406
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:27,830
I think

407
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,080
at least

408
00:24:29,370 --> 00:24:30,870
you have the right to know,

409
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,430
right?

410
00:24:34,330 --> 00:24:35,550
Let's have a word.

411
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:46,060
