413
00:24:47,350 --> 00:24:48,350
Have my jacket.

414
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,000
I'm not cold.

415
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:56,960
It's quite warm inside.

416
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,350
Why come out here?

417
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,750
Too crowded in there.

418
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,310
I don't want people to hear.

419
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:04,880
You know what I mean?

420
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,610
Family scandals stay in the family.

421
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,040
Family scandal?

422
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:10,200
Yes, it is.

423
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,790
How should I start?

424
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:18,880
Guan Aiping joined our factory
at the age of 17,

425
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:21,480
just one year older than you are now.

426
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,030
When she came,

427
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:26,070
she had beautiful braided hair.

428
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:28,000
The fellows were so excited.

429
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:29,790
"What a beautiful girl!"

430
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,480
I ran to her workshop

431
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,880
and saw her.

432
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,400
Wow, she was

433
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:36,440
incredibly pretty,

434
00:25:36,970 --> 00:25:38,030
and I fell in love.

435
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:40,070
However,

436
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,790
I didn't know what she liked.

437
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,030
No matter what I gave her,
she ignored me.

438
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,920
The way she looked at me

439
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:50,550
was just like you.

440
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,000
Later on,

441
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:55,880
Youguang came,

442
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,830
and I lost my chance.

443
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,480
Honestly, back then,

444
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:04,110
your parents were a perfect match.

445
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,510
Both pretty and capable.

446
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,790
When they walked through the factory,

447
00:26:09,270 --> 00:26:10,240
we all turned around

448
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,920
just to see them.

449
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:15,760
So,

450
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:16,840
what happened next?

451
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:19,240
Then you were born,

452
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:22,030
and Mao Tou was born too.

453
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:23,870
(Emergency Room)
You little imps

454
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:26,640
came into this bustling world.

455
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:29,240
I hung out and had fun every day,

456
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,960
while your dad worked hard

457
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,640
and even got into a college.

458
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:34,510
Back then, things were

459
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:35,630
pretty good.

460
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:38,310
Then Youguang had an accident

461
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,270
and passed away.

462
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:42,520
You and your mom

463
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,960
moved into
the Yingmo Community.

464
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,550
Honestly, at that time, I really thought

465
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:49,030
it was hard for your mom

466
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,830
to raise you alone.

467
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,790
It wasn't just me.

468
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,960
All the fellows at No. 9 Factory
felt that way.

469
00:26:54,310 --> 00:26:55,640
We respected your dad

470
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,350
and felt sorry for your mom.

471
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:59,270
We really cared about her

472
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:00,590
as her friends.

473
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:03,960
Later on,

474
00:27:05,550 --> 00:27:06,650
the factory went downhills,

475
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:09,350
and those smart people

476
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,920
began to find another living.

477
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:15,200
Mao Tou's mom went to Japan
at that time.

478
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,200
She left,

479
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:20,350
met someone, and never returned.

480
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,480
As for me,

481
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:28,720
I just gave up on myself.

482
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,240
I drank and played cards.

483
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:32,310
I gambled

484
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:33,920
and got into fights.

485
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:35,310
A total mess.

486
00:27:36,640 --> 00:27:38,920
One time, I played cards all night

487
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,880
and lost all my money.

488
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:43,270
I couldn't even afford a bowl of
rice served in soup.

489
00:27:44,030 --> 00:27:45,440
I had no choice but to go home.

490
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:48,160
When I reached the doorstep,

491
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,400
I just didn't want to go in.

492
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:50,800
Later,

493
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:53,070
I just squatted

494
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:55,590
by the flowerbed.

495
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,200
Then,

496
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:59,440
your mom came downstairs,

497
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,350
grocery shopping,

498
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:02,190
and she saw me.

499
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,440
She kept staring at me,

500
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:08,030
I felt so embarrassed.

501
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:22,080
Zhang Qiming,

502
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,510
why are you sitting here?

503
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:28,070
I lost

504
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:29,720
the key.

505
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,720
Get up,

506
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,920
I'll buy you wontons.

507
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:47,310
When I was doing business,

508
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,720
I traveled to many places.

509
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,640
I lived everywhere.

510
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:53,550
Bus stops,

511
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,790
train station benches,

512
00:28:56,110 --> 00:28:56,960
in front of shops,

513
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,000
under the bridge...

514
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:02,880
The public toilets
in Dongbei had heating.

515
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,790
Otherwise, I would've frozen to death.

516
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,750
Parks won't do,
too many mosquitoes in summer.

517
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:10,750
I often thought

518
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,310
maybe

519
00:29:14,270 --> 00:29:15,310
I'm really done for

520
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:19,310
this time.

521
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:21,550
Then I'd remember,

522
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:23,480
the wontons your mom bought for me

523
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,240
and what she said.

524
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,000
Zhang Qiming,

525
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:31,200
Mao Tou's mom has left.

526
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:35,400
Do you want him to lose his dad too?

527
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:47,640
Even as a woman, I can live well.

528
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:50,510
You're a grown man

529
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:52,850
with hands and feet.

530
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,240
Are you going to live like this?

531
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,830
I'll pay for the wontons,

532
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:10,920
but I hope you can repay me someday.

533
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:18,640
Honestly,

534
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,000
if it weren't for her,

535
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:25,160
I might not get to chat with you here.

536
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:33,980
(Emergency Room)

537
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:31,060
(Martyr Xiao Youguang,
A Role Model Like Lai Ning)

538
00:31:34,460 --> 00:31:36,000
Han, do you know when your mom

539
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,240
(Emergency Room)

540
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:39,070
lost her job?

541
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:41,950
Two years ago.

542
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:44,270
In June.

543
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:47,400
She said the factory took special care of us,

544
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:49,510
