545
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:52,920
She got laid off three years ago.

546
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:55,480
That's not true.

547
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:58,920
Three years ago, I was in Grade 9,

548
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,550
