549
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,750
The factory was closed.

550
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:03,070
How could she work there?

551
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:06,480
She'd stayed by the Suzhou River

552
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,310
for an entire day.

553
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,590
Maybe you're still young.

554
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:13,550
You might not understand
what I'm saying.

555
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:14,840
At that time,

556
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:17,160
she looked at the factory.

557
00:32:19,350 --> 00:32:20,270
It was in ruins

558
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:21,880
with locked gates.

559
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:24,480
Your mom joined the factory
at the age of 17.

560
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:26,680
She was the Red Flag Bearer every year.

561
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:29,510
But everything's gone.

562
00:32:30,030 --> 00:32:30,880
It's all gone.

563
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,160
And she had to fake a smile every day,

564
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:35,790
telling you, "Han, I'm going to work."

565
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:44,160
Han, I know

566
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,400
you don't like me.

567
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,510
I'm not as good as your dad.

568
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:49,880
That's true. I admit it.

569
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:53,350
I really can't compare to your dad.

570
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,000
But...

571
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,840
Xiao Han,

572
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:02,400
please let me take care of Aiping,

573
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:03,800
okay?

574
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,280
Your mom is quite stubborn.

575
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:11,350
If you don't agree,

576
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:13,680
she won't agree.

577
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:21,640
Dad...

578
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,040
I'm sorry.

