00:33:29,490 --> 00:33:31,200
I didn't take good care of mom.

580
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:35,480
I thought if I'm a good son

581
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,680
who studies hard

582
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:40,680
and doesn't cause trouble,

583
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:43,480
I can take care of her.

584
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:46,950
But sometimes

585
00:33:49,110 --> 00:33:50,720
I could be so powerless.

586
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,310
I want to get everything right,

587
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,750
but I really can't.

588
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:59,270
I really don't know what to do.

589
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,960
I remember the last thing
you told me.

590
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,560
You said,

591
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:08,070
"I'll protect the factory,

592
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,710
and you'll protect your mom."

593
00:34:10,510 --> 00:34:11,350
Dad,

594
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:13,360
I failed.

595
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:21,190
I'm sorry.

596
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:34,320
But you'd want her to live

597
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:37,960
a happy life,

598
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,030
right?

599
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:45,980
(Martyr Xiao Youguang,
A Role Model Like Lai Ning)

600
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:54,340
(Puyang New Village)

601
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,200
Dad.

602
00:34:58,210 --> 00:34:59,090
Qing.

603
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:00,840
Come on.

604
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,510
Careful, it's hot.

605
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,600
The buns, over there.

606
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,280
Gui.

607
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:09,000
- Hello, audience of Sunny Club.
- Okay.

608
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,000
I'm Lu Yao.

609
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,760
A new century and new millennium

610
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,600
is coming.

611
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,320
Many friends told me

612
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:15,360
they want to see it

613
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,550
as a fresh start

614
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,510
(Host, Lu Yao)
to change their lives,

615
00:35:18,770 --> 00:35:20,960
such as getting better grades,

616
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,510
becoming stronger,

617
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,510
and making more friends.

618
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:28,000
I've heard at the dawn
of the new century,

619
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,880
(Host, Lu Yao)
the first person you talk to

620
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:32,760
will have a bond with you
for a century.

621
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,400
Mom, you haven't recovered.

622
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,670
No work today.

623
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:29,190
Got it.

624
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,280
Don't worry.

625
00:36:36,550 --> 00:36:37,670
No need to cook dinner.

626
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:38,880
Mao Tou's dad said

627
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:40,400
he'd bring food today.

628
00:36:43,550 --> 00:36:44,590
I'm going to school.

629
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,640
Mom.

630
00:36:57,710 --> 00:36:58,550
Well,

631
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,710
ask him to smoke less.

632
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:03,800
When he's here, try not to smoke.

633
00:37:05,760 --> 00:37:06,920
Smoking is bad for health.

634
00:37:37,230 --> 00:37:39,150
Morning, Brother Xiao Han.

635
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:41,430
Morning, Jiayue.

636
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,150
Brother Xiao Han,

637
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:47,230
did you sleep well last night?

638
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:49,440
You seem a bit tired.

639
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,760
My mom didn't feel well.

640
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:53,000
We went to the hospital.

641
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:54,550
She didn't feel well?

642
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:56,960
Is she okay now?

643
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:57,800
She's okay.

644
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,710
She got better after the infusion.

645
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,360
That's good to hear.

646
00:38:04,890 --> 00:38:06,110
Brother Xiao Han.

647
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:07,870
What's wrong?

648
00:38:09,640 --> 00:38:10,710
I want to ask you,

649
00:38:11,630 --> 00:38:13,550
did you listen to the radio?

650
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,360
Oh, the radio.

651
00:38:17,150 --> 00:38:19,400
I was at the hospital and missed it.

652
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:21,070
Sorry.

653
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:24,440
What was I supposed to listen to?

654
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:26,920
I requested a song.

655
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:29,000
Just one song.

656
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,190
I got your message.

657
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,400
Thank you, Jiayue.

658
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:37,350
Let's go.

659
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:48,560
So sudden?

660
00:38:49,080 --> 00:38:50,510
Mrs. Xiao passed out?

661
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,190
Is she okay now?

662
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,800
She's at home.

663
00:38:54,190 --> 00:38:56,480
Brother Xiao Han said she was fine.

664
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:59,000
Why did everything happen
at the same time?

665
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:01,510
So, what's your next move?

666
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,550
Ka Men!

667
00:39:06,630 --> 00:39:07,470
Looks kinda like you?

668
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,400
- Easy! Easy!
- Look like me?

669
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,710
Nonsense!

670
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:14,190
What is this? So childish.

671
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,440
This is just a sample.

672
00:39:15,710 --> 00:39:16,580
It's the New Year's Eve.

673
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:18,110
I had a deal with Liu Jianfeng.

674
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:19,920
We'll sell the big ones at the Bund.

675
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:23,530
The stall owner next door gave me these.

676
00:39:23,550 --> 00:39:25,120
He gave me two bags to sell.

677
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:26,590
We can keep all the money we make.

678
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,670
Are you selling inflatable toys?

679
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:29,760
Yes.

680
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,000
Why don't you join us?

681
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,680
- More people, more fun.
- Okay.

682
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:34,360
I can invite Xiao to join us.

683
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:35,390
Let's go together.

684
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:36,950
What time is it?

685
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:38,240
Jiayue, Ka Men,

686
00:39:38,350 --> 00:39:39,230
let's go celebrate

687
00:39:39,230 --> 00:39:40,190
the New Year together.

688
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:42,110
- Okay.
- You're right.

689
00:39:42,110 --> 00:39:44,710
I'll ask my neighbor for two more bags.

690
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:46,110
Ask for more. We'll sell them all.

691
00:39:46,550 --> 00:39:47,920
Come early. Don't bail on me.

692
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,920
Let me see the rest.

693
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,110
That place is crowded.

694
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:53,320
The TV host said the first person

695
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,070
you talk to in the New Year

696
00:39:55,070 --> 00:39:57,670
will have a bond with you for a century.

697
00:39:58,710 --> 00:40:00,230
Xiao Han is going tonight,

698
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:01,630
so seize this opportunity.

699
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:03,550
How?

700
00:40:12,810 --> 00:40:13,990
Boyfriend?

701
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:17,550
What are you doing?

702
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:18,920
Are you slacking off?

703
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,710
I need to go to the TV station

704
00:40:21,710 --> 00:40:24,110
for the New Year's Eve Gala.
I'm almost late.

705
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:25,360
They're waiting for my rehearsal.

706
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,710
- I have to go.
- Liu Songming.

707
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:27,630
Liu Songming!

708
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:29,070
Are you going out?

709
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:29,960
- I'm heading out.
- Bye.

710
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,280
Aiping.

711
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,160
Where's Aiping?

712
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:35,840
She's ill.

713
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,510
Zhang Qiming said she passed out,

714
00:40:37,510 --> 00:40:38,350
so I gave her a day off.

715
00:40:38,710 --> 00:40:39,550
She's ill?

716
00:40:39,630 --> 00:40:40,470
Is it serious?

717
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,550
I have no idea.

718
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:43,880
What did I say?

719
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:45,960
The Millennium Bug is powerful.

720
00:40:46,190 --> 00:40:48,320
I told her to stick a talisman,

721
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,160
but she didn't do it.

722
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:51,000
Now she's suffering.

723
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,440
Where did you put it?

724
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,630
Let me check it.

725
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:58,030
Over there.

726
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,710
I'm busy.

727
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:03,800
No time for the Millennium Bug.

728
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,800
Why are you so grumpy?

729
00:41:09,110 --> 00:41:10,510
If you're busy,

730
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:12,150
ask Liu Dagui to help you.

731
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:13,150
Where did he go?

732
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:14,320
He's so impressive.

733
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,510
He's going to be on TV.

734
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,400
Pei, payment, please.

735
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:19,000
- Coming.
- Already eaten.

736
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:20,670
What TV show?

737
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:23,030
The New Year's Eve Gala.

738
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,510
The New Year's Eve Gala?

739
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:27,710
Is he going to be a star?

740
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,800
What star?

741
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:32,030
You know the amateur dance group, right?

742
00:41:32,030 --> 00:41:33,030
One singer

743
00:41:33,030 --> 00:41:34,960
and dozens of dancers.

744
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,190
- How much?
- 4.5 yuan.

745
00:41:40,190 --> 00:41:41,710
People can't even see him.

746
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:43,230
Why is he so excited?

747
00:41:43,630 --> 00:41:44,560
Handle the register.

748
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,000
I'll wipe the tables for you.

749
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,070
Go on.

750
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:48,710
Thank you so much.

751
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,960
Liu Songming went out,

752
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,150
and the kids are messing around.

753
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:55,190
She just called me and said they'd go to
the Bund for the New Year's Eve.

754
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:57,150
There are so many people.

755
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,630
Why do they have to go there?

756
00:42:00,660 --> 00:42:01,510
Welcome.

757
00:42:01,510 --> 00:42:02,960
Would you like some wontons?

758
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:04,680
Sure, sure.

759
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,400
Pei, listen,

760
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,110
you're out of touch.

761
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:10,320
Nowadays, kids

762
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:12,550
want to hang out

763
00:42:12,550 --> 00:42:13,590
with their friends

764
00:42:13,590 --> 00:42:14,630
and have some fun.

765
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,030
While I'm alone at home?

766
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:19,190
I also want to celebrate
the New Year's Eve.

767
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:22,000
Are you feeling jealous?

768
00:42:24,170 --> 00:42:26,250
How about I stay with you?

769
00:42:26,710 --> 00:42:28,800
I've got nothing to do at home.

770
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,400
Just waiting for the kids to come home.

771
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:32,000
Let's have some fun.

772
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:32,990
What do you think?

773
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:36,630
Don't you need to stay with Qian Kang?
Stop joking.

774
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,710
Qian Kang said

775
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:41,320
the business might go well tonight.

776
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:43,000
He plans to have more trips.

777
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:43,840
Auntie Huang.

778
00:42:46,190 --> 00:42:47,480
That's great.

779
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,070
This morning,

780
00:42:50,070 --> 00:42:51,760
Fangfang's husband
went on a business trip.

781
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,440
Why not invite her as well?

782
00:42:53,640 --> 00:42:54,510
Sure, no problem.

783
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:55,960
Let's invite Aiping too.

784
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:58,810
We can play mahjong together.

785
00:42:59,140 --> 00:43:00,150
Once we're done here,

786
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:01,760
I'll check on her.

787
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:02,960
Okay. Okay.

788
00:43:03,770 --> 00:43:04,700
Have some wontons.

789
00:43:04,720 --> 00:43:05,880
No need. I've already eaten.

790
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:06,880
- It's okay.
- You did?

791
00:43:07,820 --> 00:43:09,480
Have a seat. What would you like?

792
00:43:10,110 --> 00:43:11,710
We have wontons and noodles.

793
00:43:12,800 --> 00:43:14,510
Aiping, I'm back.

794
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,670
I bought an old hen

795
00:43:17,670 --> 00:43:18,880
from Small Pudong,

796
00:43:19,210 --> 00:43:20,670
I'll make chicken soup for you.

797
00:43:22,650 --> 00:43:23,510
You sneak,

798
00:43:23,510 --> 00:43:24,350
you freaked me out!

799
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:26,840
You have the key?

800
00:43:27,070 --> 00:43:28,710
How do you have the key?

801
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,340
Any problem?

802
00:43:30,350 --> 00:43:31,670
She gave it to me this morning.

803
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:35,040
Why were you here this morning?

804
00:43:38,220 --> 00:43:41,340
(End of Episode 10)

