816
00:44:47,361 --> 00:44:48,691
♪That♪

817
00:44:48,691 --> 00:44:52,711
♪Is the cost of growing up♪

818
00:44:53,001 --> 00:44:55,591
♪Learn to let go♪

819
00:44:56,281 --> 00:44:58,651
♪Learn to play dumb♪

820
00:45:00,611 --> 00:45:02,211
♪Please♪

821
