♪Learn to answer like a grown-up♪

822
00:45:06,571 --> 00:45:09,351
♪If you have an ordinary life♪

823
00:45:10,051 --> 00:45:14,131
♪Then choose to be open-minded♪

824
00:45:14,881 --> 00:45:16,141
♪Love♪

825
00:45:16,141 --> 00:45:19,911
♪May be the key♪

