00:45:21,761 --> 00:45:24,221
♪My girl♪

827
00:45:24,221 --> 00:45:27,681
♪You've cut your long hair♪

828
00:45:28,601 --> 00:45:32,981
♪Tears drop from the corner of your eyes♪

829
00:45:35,461 --> 00:45:38,091
♪One day, all alone♪

830
00:45:38,091 --> 00:45:41,461
♪You climbed a high tower♪

831
00:45:42,291 --> 00:45:47,171
♪And saw yourself growing up♪

832
00:45:49,091 --> 00:45:51,211
♪Little girl♪

833
00:45:51,211 --> 00:45:53,021
♪Don't♪

834
